{
  "arquivo": "op_02_02",
  "total": 62,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, sorry to have kept you waiting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wowww, okay!\\nTh-that's, DANGEROUS, isn't it?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I knew you would come.\\nI knew you would choose me, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino?\\nAre you crying?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I'm not crying.\\nWhy should I be crying?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But, you're shaking...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "It's because I'm happy.\\nThe moment I've been waiting for has finally come.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(She's saying that, but she's actually...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "!...\\nHey, Fu-kun? Um...\\nWhy did you hug me so tight?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I just felt like it.\\nDid it hurt?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "No, I'm fine...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun, your heart's pounding so hard.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, um...\\nY-your heart is pounding really hard too, you know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "It's because of you, Fu-kun.\\nAnd what's the reason for your heart pounding so fast...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...It's you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Teehee!\\nThat's right.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "How should I put it?\\nIt might be too late to say this now, but...\\nWell, you know...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "No way!\\nSay it properly.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino.\\nI like you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I like you too, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, um, you've already told me that before...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I wonder what's going on.\\nI never thought I'd be giving this kind of answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh really?\\nI believed that day would come for sure.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "The day where you would learn\\nhow much I love you, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's amazing about you\\nis that you really do follow through with things.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Fu-kun. Stay by my side from now on.\\nNo matter what...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Will you stay by my side too?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Huh? What do you mean by that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm just saying I'm not some kind of prince charming.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I don't really think\\nyou're dreaming that I'm a prince on a white horse\\nor anything like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Honestly, I don't think I'm cut out\\nfor the kind of relationship that most people have.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "To be honest,\\nI think I'll just disappoint you from now on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Wait, Fu-kun!\\nI%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Even so.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Even so, I want to take it a step further, Nino.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "A step further...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I've only been thinking about studying so far.\\nI can say\\nthat I've ignored everything else besides studying.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But, after meeting you quintuplets, and then%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I fell in love the first time I saw you.\\nLove was always a mystery to me,\\nbut you opened a new perspective for me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I want to keep looking at this...\\nb-beautiful world...\\nthat shines because you're here, Nino.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's...my wish...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I feel the same way too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Thanks to you, Fu-kun,\\nI got to know what love is.\\nThat's why you're important to me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Please, don't disappear.\\nStay by my side, forever.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Huh?!\\nWhat? What's wrong, Fu-kun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Nino.\\nI...won't ever leave you.\\nI'll always be by your side from now on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I'm serious, you know?\\nI swear on, my, um, what's it called again?\\nUmm, my soul! I swear on my soul...for you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Heh! Ahahahaha! The hell was THAT?\\nStop acting so tough!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Stop laughing!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Just say it without trying to act cool.\\nBecause%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I fell in love with you because you're you, Fu-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}